sys_app.name: DevOps+
sys_app.short_description: Increase your development and admin productivity by: - Search for script snippets or references in all artefacts (including Flows) via Code Search by hotkey (Win: CTRL+SHIFT+F | MacOS: CMD+SHIFT+F) - Show hidden important fields like description and scope on Application Files - Transform List-Filter-Breadcrumbs to standardized Scripts - Customizeable DevOps+ Context Menu - Translation finetuning - Best Practice Code Generation on Fields, Forms and Breadcrumbs (Lists)
